title: ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'classify'
body: I'm getting this error with line 137 of rank.py. After installing classify with `pip install classify`, I am getting another error: AttributeError: Can't get attribute 'twolayermlp'. Any idea how to fix this?

title: Unable to Operate the Program with a 4.9k Insertion
body:
Hi,

I am trying to use this program to sequence atgRNA for a 4.9k insertion. But after I put the whole sequence in the command window. The program is frozen (I think it is just running forever and I did not see the question pop out). When I try to run with some short sequence (just random sequences ~500 bp it works fine). I am kind of confused since I saw you used cargo with 4906 bp so I am not sure why mine is not working. Did I do anything wrong? Thank you very much!

Sincerely,

Ling
